sentence.Network_en: Raise a song, strike the timbrel, The sweet sounding lyre with the harp.
sentence.Network_cn: 诗81:2唱起诗歌 、 打手鼓 、 弹美琴与瑟.

sentence.Network_en: They sing to the timbrel and harp and make merry to the sound of the flute.
sentence.Network_cn: 他们伴着手鼓与竖琴歌唱,随着笛声欢呼.

sentence.Network_en: Praise him with the timbrel and dance: praise him with stringed instruments and organs.
sentence.Network_cn: 击鼓跳舞赞美他,用丝弦的乐器,和箫的声音赞美他.
